  "description": "A stunning aerial view of a clear, turquoise coastline. The water transitions from shallow, rocky terrain near the shore to a deep, dark blue in the distance.  Visible through the clear water are rocks and the seabed, creating patterns of light and shadow. The shoreline is composed of small pebbles and stones.  A darker, rocky outcrop is visible on the right side of the frame, contrasting with the bright blue and turquoise hues of the sea. The sky is a clear, bright blue without any clouds.",
